{"id": "art-25144", "label": "Art. 25144", "title": "Art. 25144", "slug": "art-25144", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1585900763\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1492\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1585900763\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>44</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_976206508\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1491\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_976206508\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Administratorii sau, dup&#259; caz, membrii\ndirectoratului întocmesc un raport, cu dou&#259; <span class=SpellE>sec&#355;iuni</span>,\nuna destinat&#259; <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cealalt&#259; destinat&#259; <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>,\nsau dou&#259; rapoarte distincte, în care explic&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\njustific&#259; aspectele juridice <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> economice\nale transform&#259;rii transfrontaliere, explicând <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n<span class=SpellE>implica&#355;iile</span> transform&#259;rii transfrontaliere\npentru <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;i</span>. Raportul precizeaz&#259;, în\nspecial, <span class=SpellE>implica&#355;iile</span> transform&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere asupra <span class=SpellE>activit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\neconomice viitoare a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_271000426\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1490\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_271000426\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În <span\nclass=SpellE>sec&#355;iunea</span> din raport destinat&#259;/În raportul\ndestinat <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> sunt precizate cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> urm&#259;toarele:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_890545658\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1489\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_890545658\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)<span class=SpellE>implica&#355;iile</span>\ntransform&#259;rii transfrontaliere pentru <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1507763433\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1488\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1507763433\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)<span class=SpellE>pre&#355;ul</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de valoare\nreprezentând capitalul social ale <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>\ncare <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> exercit&#259; dreptul de retragere din\nsocietate, inclusiv metoda de calcul al acestuia;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2102607686\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1487\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2102607686\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)drepturile de care beneficiaz&#259; <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\npotrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>49</sup>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_52011334\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1486\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_52011334\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<span class=SpellE>Sec&#355;iunea</span> din raport\ndestinat&#259;/Raportul destinat <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> nu\neste obligatorie/obligatoriu în cazul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\ncu r&#259;spundere limitat&#259; cu asociat unic sau în cazul în care <span\nclass=SpellE>to&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> au convenit s&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>renun&#355;e</span> la aceast&#259; <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;&#259;</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_891521210\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1485\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_891521210\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În <span\nclass=SpellE>sec&#355;iunea</span> din raport destinat&#259;/În raportul\ndestinat <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> sunt precizate cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> urm&#259;toarele:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1919949931\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1484\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1919949931\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)efectele transform&#259;rii transfrontaliere asupra\nraporturilor de munc&#259;, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dup&#259;\ncaz, m&#259;surile necesare pentru <span class=SpellE>men&#355;inerea</span>\nacestor raporturi de munc&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_101600377\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1483\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_101600377\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)orice modificare <span class=SpellE>substan&#355;ial&#259;</span>\na <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iilor</span> de munc&#259; sau a sediilor\nsecundare ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1336604012\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1482\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1336604012\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)modul în care elementele prev&#259;zute la lit. a) <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> b) afecteaz&#259; filialele <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1446078203\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1481\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1446078203\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)<span class=SpellE>Sec&#355;iunea</span> din raport\ndestinat&#259;/Raportul destinat <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> nu\neste obligatorie/obligatoriu în cazul în care activitatea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dac&#259; este cazul, a filialelor sale este\nderulat&#259; exclusiv de c&#259;tre administratori sau, dup&#259; caz, de\nmembrii consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> ori,\ndup&#259; caz, de membrii consiliului de supraveghere <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nai directoratului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1033063509\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1480\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1033063509\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Cu cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;ase</span> s&#259;pt&#259;mâni înainte de data întrunirii\nadun&#259;rii generale convocate s&#259; aprobe transformarea\ntransfrontalier&#259; a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\nraportul/rapoartele prev&#259;zut/prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) sau, dup&#259;\ncaz, <span class=SpellE>sec&#355;iunea</span> corespunz&#259;toare a raportului\nse pune la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span> <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;ilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> sau, în cazul în care nu au fost <span\nclass=SpellE>desemna&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;i</span>,\na <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> <span class=SpellE>în&#351;i&#351;i</span>,\ncel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> în format electronic, prin <span\nclass=SpellE>afi&#351;are</span> pe pagina de internet a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\npotrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>47</sup>\nalin. (3), sau prin transmitere pe cale electronic&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1319220013\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1479\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1319220013\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)<span class=SpellE>Reprezentan&#355;ii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> sau, dac&#259; nu au fost <span\nclass=SpellE>desemna&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;i</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>în&#351;i&#351;i</span>\nau dreptul s&#259; formuleze o opinie cu privire la raportul destinat/la <span\nclass=SpellE>sec&#355;iunea</span> din raport destinat&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> cu cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\n5 zile înainte de data întrunirii adun&#259;rii generale convocate s&#259;\naprobe proiectul de transformare transfrontalier&#259;. Opinia se anexeaz&#259;\nraportului, iar administratorii/membrii directoratului transmit r&#259;spuns\nmotivat <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span> de opinia formulat&#259; cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> cu o zi înaintea acestei date. <span\nclass=SpellE>Asocia&#355;ii</span> sunt <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;i</span>\ncu privire la opinia formulat&#259; de <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;ii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> sau, dup&#259; caz, de <span\nclass=SpellE>angaja&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>în&#351;i&#351;i</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1850116778\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1478\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1850116778\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)În cazul în care, în conformitate cu <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nalin. (3), se <span class=SpellE>renun&#355;&#259;</span> la <span\nclass=SpellE>sec&#355;iunea</span> din raport destinat&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>, iar <span class=SpellE>sec&#355;iunea</span>\ndestinat&#259; <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> nu este obligatorie\nîntrucât sunt aplicabile prevederile alin. (5), raportul nu este necesar.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1196265851\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1477\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1196265851\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Prevederile alin. (1)-(8) nu aduc atingere drepturilor <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> procedurilor de informare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nconsultare aplicabile <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>,\nprev&#259;zute de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>467/2006</span><span style='color:black'>, cu\nmodific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile\nulterioare, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>217/2005</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, republicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile ulterioare, <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nalin. (7) aplicându-se în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1696150922\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1476\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1696150922\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Administratorii sau, dup&#259; caz, membrii\ndirectoratului informeaz&#259; <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> înainte\nde data întrunirii adun&#259;rii generale convocate pentru aprobarea\ntransform&#259;rii transfrontaliere sau, cel mai târziu, în cadrul acesteia\ndac&#259;, ulterior datei întocmirii proiectului de transformare\ntransfrontalier&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a\nraportului/rapoartelor prev&#259;zut/prev&#259;zute la alin. (1), au intervenit\nmodific&#259;ri semnificative privind activele <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nsau nivelul veniturilor acesteia, în special în cazul în care acestea ar\ndetermina un <span class=SpellE>pre&#355;</span> diferit al <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de\nvaloare reprezentând capitalul social al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>"}